{"tid":1732900,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"抗爭唔係為其他人，唔係計值唔值得","createTime":"2019-11-18T03:41:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T03:46:56.000Z","uid":336563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9e281acdff650bf6d73446b90182fc856963b0f0","tid":1732900,"uid":336563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:41:56.000Z","msg":"見到D人話香港人好自私，港豬港奴心態唔值得幫<br />\n我都明白大家出心出力見到班人仲掛住返工吃喝玩樂<br />\n係會好激氣<br />\n<br />\n但係抗爭係咪就只係計較值唔值得？<br />\n決定堅唔堅持抗爭係用呢d野衡量？<br />\n我地選擇抗爭係因為唔想向極權低頭<br />\n係咪因爲身邊既人放棄接受極權，我地就放棄呢？<br />\n唔好再分化抱怨，場仗已經好難打<br />\n灰心一定難免，<br />\n但無論點都唔好放棄<br />\n<br />\n希望經過琴日傷心既一晚，大家可以再次振作"},{"pid":"51d7ccd0a1e9b89bbe369f5770dd9b594a5ca624","tid":1732900,"uid":125502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:43:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s9ZjRtg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs9ZjRtg.jpg&h=edebd45e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n緊急呼籲<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">你仲返工？去佐敦啦！</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不落單<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不譴責<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不退縮"},{"pid":"51dd6fe62356ef19ec2fdc6837e33c085a19327e","tid":1732900,"uid":13600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:46:56.000Z","msg":"請所有現任立法會議員及區議員（包候侯選人），立即聯合展開營救理大工作<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1732805\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1732805</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}